X Platform - Teacher Dashboard System Documentation
Project Overview

X Platform is an advanced e-learning platform designed initially for Jordanian Tawjihi students.

The platform currently focuses on Arabic and English subjects, with future support for scalable educational systems, advanced streaming protection, AI-powered educational assistance, and multi-role dashboard architecture.

This stage introduces the complete Teacher Dashboard System, Teacher Course Management Architecture, Lesson Management System, Video Management Infrastructure, Teacher Profile System, and role-isolated teacher permissions.

Teacher Dashboard Overview
Purpose

The Teacher Dashboard was designed to provide teachers with a fully isolated management environment.

Teachers can:

Manage their own courses
Manage lessons
Upload and connect videos
Manage lesson resources
Edit profile information
Change account password
Monitor course content

Teachers CANNOT:

Access admin-only management systems
Manage other teachers' courses
Access global platform administration
Manage users outside their permissions
